match_description: Non‑tech founder meets an engineer who can own the tech stack—idea + coding = complete team.

profiles.raw_input: Hi, I'm Olivia Parker, founder of HealthTrack, a health monitoring app that helps users track and analyze their wellness data. I have a business background and a clear vision for the product but I'm looking for a technical co-founder who can build and lead our tech stack. My app idea has received positive feedback from early testers, but I need a skilled engineer to turn this vision into reality.

personal.name: Olivia Parker
personal.headline: Founder of HealthTrack - Seeking Technical Co-Founder

roles.title: Founder & CEO
highlights: Conducted market research and validated product concept
Secured initial seed funding from angel investors
Developed MVP wireframes and user journey maps

roles.title: Healthcare Marketing Director
highlights: Led marketing strategies for healthcare technology products
Managed product launches and market expansions

profiles.extra_notes: Non-technical founder with strong business acumen and industry connections, looking specifically for a technical co-founder who can build our product from the ground up.

profiles.raw_input: Hello, I'm Marcus Chen, a senior software engineer with extensive full-stack development experience. I've built and scaled multiple applications from the ground up and led engineering teams at tech companies. While I enjoy coding, I'm now looking to join an early-stage startup as a technical co-founder where I can build and own the entire tech stack. I'm particularly interested in health tech and would love to find a visionary founder with domain expertise.

personal.name: Marcus Chen
personal.headline: Senior Software Engineer - Looking for Co-founder Opportunity

roles.title: Senior Software Engineer
highlights: Architected and built scalable web applications from scratch
Led backend team for company's flagship product
Implemented CI/CD pipelines that reduced deployment time by 60%

profiles.extra_notes: Ready to take on a CTO role in an early-stage startup. Looking for a non-technical founder with a strong vision and business expertise who needs someone to build their product.
